{"tid":543132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"17歲DSE考生　墮樓亡","createTime":"2018-01-28T07:38:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-28T07:44:16.000Z","uid":137233,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4dd20d50e1b568d5f9eb4bacd0d39c9267242d2f","tid":543132,"uid":137233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T07:38:51.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】一名DSE考生墮樓亡！前晚10時許，葵涌葵盛東邨，一名姓陳17歲少女從高處墮下，倒臥盛逸樓對開，重傷昏迷。救護人員接報趕到將事主送院搶救，惜終告不治。警方在停車場五樓平台發現一對拖鞋，相信她由該處墮下。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息指，女事主是一名中六女生，在青衣一間中間讀書，成續名列前茅，是應屆DSE考生，疑考試壓力困擾，加上事發前與家人爭執。警方於現場沒有撿獲遺書，調查事件沒有可疑。<br />\n<br />\n街坊稱，死者與父母及胞姐同住，父親任職超市司機，母親為家庭主婦，間日做兼職；胞姐則在區內工作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180128/20288190\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180128%2F20288190&d=1Whq721RRDjtmRFbjUE4gjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=411fe31a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180128%2F20288190&h=583eeed0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180128/20288190</a><br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288"},{"pid":"57c583c85991c628d1960dd592af3055be2f13bc","tid":543132,"uid":39181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T07:41:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbcf1ab38e7fa2dd6d2ed2633ad0bd3ae2b4f5fc","tid":543132,"uid":6869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T07:42:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8d7690500ddc5a44899cc5bce31dba1bf53288ee","tid":543132,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T07:44:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}